Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.86,0:00:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inherited will...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.53,0:00:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The tide of the times... People's dreams...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.41,0:00:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}These things cannot be stopped.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.20,0:00:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As long as people seek the answer of freedom,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.29,0:00:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}these things will never cease to be!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.59,0:00:41.97,OP2-Romaji,,0,0,0,,mirai dake shinjiteru dareka ga warattemo kamawanai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.97,0:00:47.47,OP2-Romaji,,0,0,0,,hashitteru jounetsu ga anata o kiramekaseru
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.47,0:00:53.48,OP2-Romaji,,0,0,0,,mabushi sugi, demo mitsumete itai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.48,0:00:56.98,OP2-Romaji,,0,0,0,,dokka "bigaku" kanjiteru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.31,0:01:03.68,OP2-Romaji,,0,0,0,,dare ni mo nitenai yume no senaka o
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.68,0:01:06.93,OP2-Romaji,,0,0,0,,oikakete oikaketeku
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.93,0:01:10.22,OP2-Romaji,,0,0,0,,doramatikku te ni ireru made
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.13,0:01:22.28,OP2-Romaji,,0,0,0,,dare ni mo mienai yume no katachi o
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.28,0:01:25.36,OP2-Romaji,,0,0,0,,tsukamaete tsukamaeteku
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.36,0:01:31.35,OP2-Romaji,,0,0,0,,watashi wa tsuite yuku kara atsui kimochi
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.35,0:01:34.44,OP2-Romaji,,0,0,0,,tsujitsuma awase betsu ni iranai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.44,0:01:37.81,OP2-Romaji,,0,0,0,,arifureta nichijou yori mo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.81,0:01:41.05,OP2-Romaji,,0,0,0,,paradaisu mezashite hashire
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.59,0:00:41.97,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,{\q2}I only believe in the future, I don't care if anyone laughs
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.97,0:00:47.47,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,that racing passion makes you shine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.47,0:00:53.48,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,it's too bright, but I want to gaze at it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.48,0:00:56.98,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,I sense "aesthetics" somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.31,0:01:03.68,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,I follow, follow in the footsteps of a dream
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.68,0:01:06.93,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,that resembles no one
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.93,0:01:10.22,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,until I dramatically get it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.13,0:01:22.28,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,I'm going to catch, catch the shape
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.28,0:01:25.36,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,of a dream no one can see
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.36,0:01:31.35,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,I'm going to go with you, so passionate feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.35,0:01:34.44,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,I don't really need everything to add up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.44,0:01:37.81,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,rather than run-of-the-mill daily life,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.81,0:01:41.05,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,run for paradise instead
Dialogue: 10,0:01:51.36,0:01:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Sickle-Sickle...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:53.40,0:01:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,...Whirlwind!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:55.57,0:01:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oww!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:57.24,0:01:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,A wind slash!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:59.03,0:02:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Here they come! Here they come!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:01.36,0:02:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:09.29,0:02:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you escape...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:12.21,0:02:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:19.80,0:02:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Set sail for Lost Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.77,0:02:37.78,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(2000,2000)\pos(352,115)}A Solitary Island \Nin the Distant Sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.77,0:02:37.78,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(2000,2000)\pos(352,405)}The Legendary Lost Island
Dialogue: 10,0:02:39.53,0:02:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Contacting all squad captains!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:41.53,0:02:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Assemble on the deck of Ship #1!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:43.66,0:02:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the resource manager?!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:45.41,0:02:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn the yard this way!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:46.87,0:02:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no! To the right!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:48.58,0:02:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Go get repair planks from the other ships!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:51.42,0:02:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Repair Team! \NGet to work repairing Ship #1!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:56.46,0:02:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Those damn pirates...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:58.43,0:03:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,They're quicker at running than I expected.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:01.47,0:03:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,No worries. \NIt'd be best to let them go for now, anyway.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:05.22,0:03:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:06.43,0:03:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,They went to such dangerous lengths \Nto escape from this island.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:10.44,0:03:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you think that is?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:12.81,0:03:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you forgotten this island has a legend?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:15.86,0:03:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The story about the dragons' nest on Lost Island...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:19.86,0:03:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Are you saying they...?!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:22.45,0:03:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only a guess.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:26.08,0:03:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But if so, they'll wind up being the perfect guides there.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:37.17,0:03:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Reporting to Commodore Nelson?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:39.72,0:03:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:42.76,0:03:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,There will be no need for that.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:44.47,0:03:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir! But...!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:52.56,0:03:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Dragonite I seek... \NThe elixir of immortality...{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:56.54,0:03:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As if I'd ever hand it over \Nto the likes of Nelson Royal!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:01.61,0:04:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will have it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:03.69,0:04:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To become a flawless Eric the Whirlwind!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:12.91,0:04:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What's taking so long?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:18.00,0:04:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Commodore, sir! Please have this!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:22.34,0:04:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what I mean!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:25.47,0:04:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Commodore Nelson Royal!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:26.72,0:04:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! It's about time!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:30.10,0:04:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a report from Eric, I assume?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:32.60,0:04:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,No. It's a message from a soldier \Nworking at Warship Island.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:36.77,0:04:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,"Eric has located the \Nlegendary Millennial Dragon."
Dialogue: 10,0:04:39.73,0:04:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,He goes on to say that all ships \Nare presently busy repairing damage
Dialogue: 10,0:04:42.24,0:04:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,that the flagship received.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:44.82,0:04:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Curse you, Eric...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:47.32,0:04:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Why've you not reported to me \Nafter finding the Millennial Dragon?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:52.29,0:04:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you planning to take the \NDragonite all for yourself?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:57.25,0:05:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You're nothing more than a hired soldier.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:06.05,0:05:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Our main forces will now \Nhead for Warship Island!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:09.89,0:05:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,All ships, move out!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:25.20,0:05:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Lost Island, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:28.95,0:05:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The map doesn't have any islands \Nin the waters around Warship Island
Dialogue: 10,0:05:32.12,0:05:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,that fit the bill...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:34.87,0:05:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Grandpa Ryu!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:37.08,0:05:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Which way should we go?!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:57.44,0:05:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:01.61,0:06:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I think he went to sleep again!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:08.45,0:06:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the wait, everyone!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:10.95,0:06:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The food's ready!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:12.99,0:06:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Did she cook again?!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:15.16,0:06:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No one was waiting for {\i1}her{\i0} food!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:20.50,0:06:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Sanji!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:22.50,0:06:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Whew, what a relief!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:24.09,0:06:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So {\i1}you{\i0} made today's meal...?!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:28.34,0:06:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa Ryu!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:30.14,0:06:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat lots, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:31.73,0:06:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Food!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:34.68,0:06:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Food!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:37.85,0:06:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hot!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:40.31,0:06:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you...!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:48.70,0:06:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hot!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:50.20,0:06:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa Ryu!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:51.36,0:06:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Apis!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:56.54,0:06:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa Ryu!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:16.72,0:07:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa Ryu!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:18.52,0:07:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:25.86,0:07:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Sheesh. \NI made all that food and it goes to waste!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:29.74,0:07:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you just make some more, then?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:31.82,0:07:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The point is we shouldn't waste food!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:39.79,0:07:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:45.50,0:07:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Lost Island...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:47.55,0:07:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The dragons' nest... \NIt's east of Warship Island...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:51.72,0:07:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's where Lost Island is?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:53.84,0:07:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa Ryu said he just remembered!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:59.89,0:08:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We know where!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:01.77,0:08:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Lost Island is east of Warship Island!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:04.94,0:08:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa Ryu said so!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.02,0:08:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:08.27,0:08:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Usopp! Take the wheel!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:10.27,0:08:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You got it!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:13.86,0:08:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! \NLet's rush straight for Lost Island!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:26.54,0:08:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit! You better eat all of that!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:28.55,0:08:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep! Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:32.09,0:08:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,They've changed course?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:33.84,0:08:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir! The pirate ship appears \Nto be headed for the waters
Dialogue: 10,0:08:36.43,0:08:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,east of Warship Island!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:40.27,0:08:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So they're making their move...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:46.23,0:08:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn the bows eastward! \NFull speed ahead!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:49.40,0:08:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We're now going to close \Nin on the Straw Hat Pirates!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:53.32,0:08:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Cannoneers to the gun batteries!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:54.70,0:08:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,All ships, prepare for Level 3 combat!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:57.12,0:08:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Our destination...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:58.58,0:09:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,...is Lost Island.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:01.33,0:09:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,All ships, move out!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:08.17,0:09:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, Zoro.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:09.09,0:09:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:11.38,0:09:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go, Zoro.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:12.30,0:09:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:14.67,0:09:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, Zoro.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:15.55,0:09:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:18.30,0:09:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Zoro.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:19.26,0:09:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:21.97,0:09:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, Zoro.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:23.77,0:09:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you hand 'em to me without talking?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:30.86,0:09:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Lost Island is at the end of this great ocean!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:35.15,0:09:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of island could it be?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:37.66,0:09:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:39.36,0:09:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Usopp! See anything?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:42.20,0:09:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope, nothing!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:43.87,0:09:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,No?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:46.58,0:09:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, we've come a long way, \Nbut there's no sign of an island at all...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:51.92,0:09:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we sure about this?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:52.96,0:09:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:54.51,0:09:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And then there's Grandpa Ryu...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:56.76,0:09:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish he'd remember some \Nmore details or something...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:00.76,0:10:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! I know!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:04.06,0:10:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's bonk Grandpa Ryu in the head with this!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:06.64,0:10:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Think maybe then the shock'll \Nhelp him remember something else?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:09.31,0:10:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Knock it off!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:25.37,0:10:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Grandpa Ryu! We're almost there!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:27.33,0:10:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We're almost to Lost Island!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:30.38,0:10:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's there, right? The dragons' nest?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:32.63,0:10:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you go to the dragons' nest, \Nyou'll get better, right?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:38.34,0:10:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:41.68,0:10:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so goofy, thanking me!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:43.93,0:10:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not even there yet!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:05.08,0:11:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,They followed us, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:08.66,0:11:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that? Smoke?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:19.42,0:11:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well! We'll see when we get closer!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:22.26,0:11:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Urgh!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:24.00,0:11:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true! \NI don't think you're troubling me at all!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:28.02,0:11:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your problem?!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:29.27,0:11:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,– It turned into an argument at some point.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:29.27,0:11:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,– Hey! Grandpa Ryu!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:31.31,0:11:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,– Hey! Are you listening?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:31.81,0:11:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,– It looks more like Apis is
Dialogue: 10,0:11:32.60,0:11:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,– Pretending to sleep isn't fair!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:33.31,0:11:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,– the only one who's angry, though...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:34.81,0:11:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,– Hey, say something!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:35.48,0:11:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,– Do you think we should stop her?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:44.28,0:11:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,A... ship?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:46.57,0:11:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But something's definitely not right about it...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:05.05,0:12:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Awesome! Nami! Check it out!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:08.39,0:12:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I already {\i1}am{\i0}...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:11.02,0:12:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! Look at me!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:25.53,0:12:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,– The pirate ship! \N– This can't be real!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:28.37,0:12:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What the...?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:29.82,0:12:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It vanished!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:31.87,0:12:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:34.12,0:12:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What just happened?! \NWhy did they disappear?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:37.91,0:12:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I have no idea!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:41.76,0:12:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,– All ships, full stop! \N– Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:43.05,0:12:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell everyone to wait on \Nstandby until my next orders!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:45.30,0:12:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:46.05,0:12:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Continue moving forward.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:47.93,0:12:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't be serious! \NThere's no telling what's in the waters ahead!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:52.02,0:12:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too risky!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:53.64,0:12:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That again?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:59.65,0:13:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Then have them prepare a small craft.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:02.69,0:13:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not seriously going to...!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:05.57,0:13:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. I'm going on my own.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:27.80,0:13:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? It's just fog...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:29.82,0:13:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought Nami was in big \Ntrouble again or something...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:33.56,0:13:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the world's going on?!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:35.64,0:13:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What {\i1}was{\i0} that?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:39.07,0:13:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Our own ship was right in front of us...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:41.77,0:13:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And then we went right through it... right?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:43.94,0:13:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't see anything at all!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:46.24,0:13:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It was almost like... a mirage...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:49.03,0:13:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,A mirage? That's it!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:51.24,0:13:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I read about this a long time ago!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:53.16,0:13:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It said temperature differences \Nbetween warm and cold ocean water
Dialogue: 10,0:13:56.13,0:13:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,can create mirages at sea!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:10.05,0:14:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this a mirage, too?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:12.01,0:14:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Urgh! What's the deal with this sea?!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:21.61,0:14:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit! What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:23.82,0:14:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! \NI can't help it, you damn bastard!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:27.03,0:14:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanji-{\i1}kun{\i0}! Zoro!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:28.99,0:14:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's raise the sails! Undo the ropes!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:31.20,0:14:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Nami-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:32.73,0:14:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You stay in the cabin!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:34.16,0:14:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No! \NI'm going to stay by Grandpa Ryu's side!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:37.12,0:14:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot! \NThere's nothing you can do by staying with him!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:39.96,0:14:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he's feeling lonesome! \NI hafta hurry to him!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:43.42,0:14:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:47.09,0:14:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Just sit down and shut up!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:57.23,0:15:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry! We need to hurry back \Ndown and get out of danger!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:04.40,0:15:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,For some reason it seems...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:06.23,0:15:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,...like this sea's trying to push the ship back.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:12.78,0:15:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa Ryu!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:15.12,0:15:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa Ryu!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:16.79,0:15:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry! This storm is no big deal at...!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:30.84,0:15:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:36.72,0:15:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Zoro!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:46.98,0:15:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa Ryu! No! What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:50.41,0:15:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We {\i1}will{\i0} save you! Don't give up!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:58.87,0:16:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We promised we'd go to your nest together!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:02.79,0:16:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:04.92,0:16:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...Lasso!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:08.38,0:16:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami-{\i1}san{\i0}! There's light over there!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:10.34,0:16:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the eye of the typhoon!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:12.51,0:16:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! I see an island below that light!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:15.68,0:16:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to land there!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:19.64,0:16:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:21.01,0:16:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry! Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:23.39,0:16:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We're taking him to the dragons' nest, right?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:26.61,0:16:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:35.20,0:16:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Stormy seas surround the island...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:39.74,0:16:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost like they're trying \Nto keep people away from it...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:43.66,0:16:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That must be why nobody's \Never found it before, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:48.08,0:16:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But it seems more like a castle that's sunk into the sea than an island...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:56.09,0:16:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! Check it out!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:58.22,0:17:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't that seem shaped like a dragon?!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:00.31,0:17:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,This must be where the \NMillennial Dragon lives after all!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:03.77,0:17:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! Dragons sure are skillful!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:07.27,0:17:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot! \NIt was obviously humans who made this building!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:11.33,0:17:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, whatever.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:13.81,0:17:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We made it to Lost Island!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:20.91,0:17:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But does anyone even live here anymore?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:24.24,0:17:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The whole place has been \Nswallowed up by Mother Nature...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:26.76,0:17:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, where do you suppose the dragons' nest is?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:29.84,0:17:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:31.30,0:17:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa Ryu! \NI'm talking to you, Grandpa Ryu!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:34.22,0:17:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Sheesh! \NWe're at the dragon nest island now!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:37.13,0:17:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, wake up!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:44.77,0:17:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What did he say?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:47.35,0:17:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He says he's not sure...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:49.18,0:17:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He says this might {\i1}not{\i0} be Lost Island...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:52.48,0:17:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:53.65,0:17:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't be serious!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:54.94,0:17:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We went all the way through \Nthat stormy sea just to get here!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:59.74,0:18:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Apis!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:01.78,0:18:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at the top there!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:03.74,0:18:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We could look down at the \Nwhole island from up there!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:06.29,0:18:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Trying to figure things \Nout here won't get us anywhere!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:09.50,0:18:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go have a look!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:10.50,0:18:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:11.17,0:18:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! Let's go!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:20.09,0:18:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Stupid Nami makes the men do all the work...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:24.06,0:18:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like, "Try pushing it yourself!"
Dialogue: 10,0:18:25.77,0:18:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you! \NLess complaining and more pushing!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:28.77,0:18:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't start getting cocky, you!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:30.61,0:18:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit complaining and push!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:32.57,0:18:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! \NNami-{\i1}san{\i0} is so nice when she's snappy!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:35.28,0:18:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,If only!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:46.20,0:18:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a city...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:50.50,0:18:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! Everything is broken everywhere!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:54.80,0:18:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Did people really used to live here?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:57.26,0:19:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Obviously, given all of these houses.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:00.05,0:19:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why's there no one here now?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:02.30,0:19:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows? \NMaybe they found a better island to live on.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:10.48,0:19:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The Millennial Dragon's mark...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:13.23,0:19:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Did the Millennial Dragon play \Nwith children here on this island?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:19.82,0:19:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Are you guys friends \Nof the Millennial Dragon too?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:24.78,0:19:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Apis. Don't get left behind!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:29.54,0:19:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess what?! \NThese birds told me something!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:32.33,0:19:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,They said there's a building \Non the summit with a dragon mark!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:35.92,0:19:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,For reals?!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:37.35,0:19:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It might be the dragons' nest!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:44.85,0:19:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:49.18,0:19:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait for me!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:04.16,0:20:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready... go!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:08.87,0:20:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We finally made it... I can't go on...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:12.54,0:20:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for showing us the way!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:17.75,0:20:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We've sure come up a long ways.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:20.01,0:20:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Good work, everyone!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:22.13,0:20:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep! Good work!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:26.85,0:20:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This painting is of the Millennial Dragon, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:29.43,0:20:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it is.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:31.60,0:20:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,This building is the dragons' nest?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:34.18,0:20:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This{\i0} place?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:35.60,0:20:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on! Where's the entrance? \NHow do we get inside?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:39.82,0:20:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This{\i0} is the door!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:41.24,0:20:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so stupid!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:42.53,0:20:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no handle or keyhole anywhere!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:44.95,0:20:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,How're you supposed to open it?!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:55.08,0:20:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:56.13,0:21:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Apis! That pendant... You don't mean...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:00.67,0:21:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's actually a key that opens \Nthe door to the dragons' nest?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:06.26,0:21:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:13.18,0:21:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:18.94,0:21:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't reach...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:21.57,0:21:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so little, Apis!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:23.07,0:21:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So what?!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:24.41,0:21:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:27.82,0:21:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:29.37,0:21:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:03.44,0:22:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We're alive... right?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:06.61,0:22:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it seems that way...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:08.94,0:22:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, what was that about it \Nbeing a key just a minute ago?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:15.37,0:22:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:19.58,0:22:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, in any case, we're inside now.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:24.26,0:22:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It worked out!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:26.22,0:22:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But... what {\i1}is{\i0} this place?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:30.26,0:22:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... What {\i1}is{\i0} it?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:40.73,0:22:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What is {\i1}this{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.06,0:23:01.90,ED2-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fscx129.8\fad(150,150)}hamidashita kimochi tsunagara nakute
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.90,0:23:06.73,ED2-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fscx129.8\fad(150,150)}kimi no te o gyutto ni girikaesu yo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.74,0:23:11.63,ED2-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fscx129.8\fad(150,150)}hitori demo boku wa arukidasu kara
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.64,0:23:16.62,ED2-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fscx129.8\fad(150,150)}tooku made zutto mitsumeteite ne
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.62,0:23:26.42,ED2-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fscx129.8\fad(150,150)}kesa kara chotto kangaeteita
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.42,0:23:31.42,ED2-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fscx129.8\fad(150,150)}doushite konna ni atsui no
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.42,0:23:37.60,ED2-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fscx129.8\fad(150,150)}itsu kara ka sonna koto bakari ga
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.60,0:23:41.43,ED2-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fscx129.8\fad(150,150)}hanarenai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.73,0:23:47.75,ED2-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fscx129.8\fad(150,150)}kakedashita kimochi tsukamaetakute
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.75,0:23:52.58,ED2-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fscx129.8\fad(150,150)}jibun sae mou oikoshite yuku yo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.58,0:23:57.33,ED2-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fscx129.8\fad(150,150)}tobidashita yume o dakishimetetai
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.32,0:24:02.83,ED2-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fscx129.8\fad(150,150)}issho nara boku wa hashitte yukeru
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.06,0:23:01.90,ED2-English,,0,0,0,,{\fscx129.8\fad(150,150)}my overflowing feelings don't connect
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.90,0:23:06.73,ED2-English,,0,0,0,,{\fscx129.8\fad(150,150)}as I firmly squeeze your hand back
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.74,0:23:11.63,ED2-English,,0,0,0,,{\fscx129.8\fad(150,150)}I'll set off by myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.64,0:23:16.62,ED2-English,,0,0,0,,{\fscx129.8\fad(150,150)}so keep watching me intently as I go into the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.62,0:23:26.42,ED2-English,,0,0,0,,{\fscx129.8\fad(150,150)}I was thinking about it a bit since this morning
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.42,0:23:31.42,ED2-English,,0,0,0,,{\fscx129.8\fad(150,150)}why is it so hot?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.42,0:23:37.60,ED2-English,,0,0,0,,{\fscx129.8\fad(150,150)}starting from some point,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.60,0:23:41.43,ED2-English,,0,0,0,,{\fscx129.8\fad(150,150)}I haven't been able to get away from that
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.73,0:23:47.75,ED2-English,,0,0,0,,{\fscx129.8\fad(150,150)}I want to catch those feelings that rushed off,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.75,0:23:52.58,ED2-English,,0,0,0,,{\fscx129.8\fad(150,150)}and I'm already about to overtake myself, even
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.58,0:23:57.33,ED2-English,,0,0,0,,{\fscx129.8\fad(150,150)}I want to embrace my dreams that have jumped out
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.32,0:24:02.83,ED2-English,,0,0,0,,{\fscx129.8\fad(150,150)}with you, I can run there
Dialogue: 10,0:24:11.86,0:24:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, now! Is this really Lost Island?!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:14.28,0:24:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,See! Look at that! This means...
Dialogue: 10,0:24:16.45,0:24:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:17.20,0:24:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That bastard! \NHe followed us all the way here?!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:20.20,0:24:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! Let's fight! You too, Zoro!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:22.00,0:24:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I said stop already!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:23.96,0:24:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! Now there's a huge armada!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:26.54,0:24:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, on One Piece:
